ArchitecturyÔÇÖs official docs provide structured ÔÇťhow-toÔÇŁ pages for major subsystems (events, registries, networking, etc.). ţłÇciteţłéturn14search0ţłéturn17view0ţłéturn17view1ţłéturn18view4ţłü They are not an exhaustive Javadoc mirror.

For v13.0.8, ArchitecturyÔÇÖs Maven directory listing shows a compiled jar and a sources jar (and checksums), but does not show a javadoc jar in that directory listing. ţłÇciteţłéturn26view0ţłü As a result, the closest thing to a ÔÇťfull API referenceÔÇŁ is typically:
