import com.example.examplemod.PlatformHooks;

public final class PlatformHooksImpl extends PlatformHooks {
    public static String getLoaderName() {
        return "fabric";
    }
}
```

```java
// neoforge/src/main/java/com/example/examplemod/neoforge/PlatformHooksImpl.java
